:"카스미","body":"이거 봐봐!\n이거! 멋지지~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"jaan01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"memorial174-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"이건 있지, 불꽃놀이 때 야시장에서 뽑은 거야~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"memorial174-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"실은 불꽃놀이가 시작하기 전에 가고 싶었는데\n애들이랑 떨어져 버려서 못 갔어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"memorial174-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"그래서 결국 돌아가는 길에 들렀는데\n그때 뽑았어!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"memorial174-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"{{userName}} 씨……\n「상어 낚시」라는 거…… 알아?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"memorial174-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"맞아, 낚는 거야!\n장난감 상어를……!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"memorial174-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"그런데 그 상어 입에 뽑기가 들어 있었는데\n거기서 이 팔찌가 당첨됐어~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"memorial174-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"자, 이거 봐봐~!\n반짝반짝하는 게 예쁘지?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"memorial174-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"건전지를 넣는 거라서 몇 번이든 쓸 수 있는 데다가\n무엇보다도!\n다섯 개나 들어 있었어!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"memorial174-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"그래서 팝핀파 멤버들이랑 다른 색으로\n다 같이 하나씩 나눠 가졌어!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"memorial174-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"인파가 엄청났지만, 이 팔찌를 손에 넣었으니까\n잘된 거지!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"memorial174-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"이 팔찌를 보고 있으면……\n그날 있었던 일들이 선~명하게 떠올라.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"memorial174-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"반짝거리는 불꽃의 빛.\n몸에 울려 퍼지는 소리.\n그리고…… 모두의 얼굴!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"m